<%= render 'shared/title' %>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <%= image_tag "logo_white_239x50.png", class: "landing-page-logo" %>
  <span class="pull-right">
    <%= link_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path, class: "sign-in-label" %>
    <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-rocket fa-2x white'></i>".html_safe,
                new_user_session_path,
                class: "sign-in-icon" %> 
  </span>
  <%#= render 'shared/share_buttons' %>
  <br>
  <h1>
    Master Your Priorities
  </h1>
  <h2>Make choices. Stay focused. Track actions.</h2>
  <div class="sign-up-button col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
    <br><br>
    <%= link_to "Start Today", new_user_registration_path, { class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg centered", id: "sign-up" } %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container landing-page" id="learnmore">
  <br><br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h3>Rakepage is an online tool for personal leadership. Rake in your potential and achieve your goals.</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2>Step 1</h2>
      <h3>Make Choices</h3>
      <p class="centered"><i class="fa fa-space-shuttle fa-2x"></i></p>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="landing-quote">
          Begin doing what you want to do now. We are not living in eternity. We have only this moment, sparkling like a star in our hand and melting like a snowflake.
        </p>
        <footer class="pull-right">Sir Francis Bacon</footer>
      </blockquote>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        You rarely have time for everything you want in this life, so you need to make choices. Rakepage is the place to refresh your awareness and take actions to achieve your goals.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2>Step 2</h2>
      <h3>Stay Focused</h3>
      <p class="centered"><i class="fa fa-bullseye fa-2x"></i></p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        In the age of distractions we are drowning in a sea of irrelevance. Focus on your priorities and take back control of what information you want to consume.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <h2>Step 3</h2>
      <h3>Track Actions</h3>
      <p class="centered"><i class="fa fa-tasks fa-2x"></i></p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        There is no substitute to improving your skills and knowledge to achieve your goals. Create personal leadership and make tracking your actions a routine.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br><hr><br><br><br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
      <%= link_to "Take a look", master_rakes_path, { class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg centered", id: "take-a-look" } %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br><br><br>
</div>

